room_title: Escape room "Magic Wonderland" by FLEE in Seattle
review: Did the Magic Wonderland room as a family and successfully escaped! Had a wonderful time! Wasn’t so difficult that my 8-year-old couldn’t participate, yet the adults in the room, a few experienced game room connoisseurs, found it challenging. We will definitely return!

room_title: Escape room "Magic Wonderland" by FLEE in Seattle
review: This is a great place to bring family and friends. We came here and had a blast! (We did the Magic Wonderland room with family of 4 and my wife.) The technology is cool and staff were really friendly. We will come back again!

room_title: Escape room "Magic Wonderland" by FLEE in Seattle
review: Did test runs for 2 rooms and I would say the puzzle designers really put lots of thoughts into the rooms. It is not something only hardcore puzzle solvers can enjoy, but people with various skill-sets and experience levels would equally have a fun time.
